snippet.title: Temukung: Cultivation in Drylands | Southeast Asia Games Onward 2024 Cut Trailer
snippet.description:
Live on driest land in Indonesia, The Timorese adapted this difficult situation with corn’s cultivation, but the imperialism created disruption in Timor. Now get ready to manage Timor’s farming as Temukung and face many difficult situations in Timor from middle 19th century until World War II
